data.description: Welcome to this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom single-family home located just off Halsted and minutes from shopping! The property has a spacious living room, a dining room, and a kitchen that is ready for customization. Additionally, the property has a lower-level family room, a laundry area, and an exit to the rear of the home. The property is on two lots with ample amount of space to do anything you can think of!
